# MyBudget

A minimalist budget tracking app built with **React Native** and **Expo**.

## 🚀 Features
- Add, update, and delete budget items
- User authentication with token-based authorization
- Elegant and minimalist UI
- Built using **React Native** and **Expo**

## 📦 Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React Native (Expo)
- **Backend:** Spring Boot (External API)
- **Database:** PostgreSQL

## 🔧 Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
Ensure you have the following installed:
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (LTS recommended)
- [Expo CLI](https://docs.expo.dev/get-started/installation/)
- [Git](https://git-scm.com/)

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```sh
git clone https://github.com/insectdie/mybudget-mobile-expo
cd mybudget-mobile-expo
```

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies
```sh
npm install # or yarn install
```

